wiki.summary: On track 11 from his third solo studio album “american dream” “prove it”, 21 Savage raps about his relationship with a woman over a soulful sentimental beat. The song features Summer Walker, being their fourth collaboration. “prove it” debuted and peaked at #43 on the Billboard Hot 100 for the chart week ending January 27, 2024. Read more on Last.fm.
